	<title>EDoc Documentation</title>
	
	<para>
		This is the documentation of the <emphasis>EDoc</emphasis> tool which can generate
		an API description of an Eiffel library or system.
	</para>
	<para>
		EDoc features are:
		<blockquote>
			<variablelist>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- Eiffel Compiler indipendent since the GOBO Eiffel parser is used
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- Can create documentation for libraries which don't fully compile with other compilers (the GOBO Eiffel parser just drops errorneous parts)
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- Can create a documentation page for each cluster with an additional cluster documentation
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- Customiseable through option files
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- HTML Output customisable through CSS file
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
				<varlistentry>
					<term>
						- HTML Output conforms to XHTML 1.1
					</term>
				</varlistentry>
			</variablelist>
		</blockquote>
	</para>
